<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/2/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/2/version/0/ayat/1/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/2/version/0/ayat/1/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/2/version/0/ayat/1/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "pemerataan hak," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/2/version/0/ayat/1/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/2/version/0/ayat/1/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/2/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/2/version/0/ayat/1/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/2/version/0/ayat/1/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/2/version/0/ayat/1/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "kepastian hukum:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/2/version/0/ayat/1/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/2/version/0/ayat/1/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/2/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/2/version/0/ayat/1/point/c> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/2/version/0/ayat/1/point/c> legal:pointHasKey "c" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/2/version/0/ayat/1/point/c/text> legal:textHasTextString "kemudahan berusaha:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/2/version/0/ayat/1/point/c> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/2/version/0/ayat/1/point/c/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/2/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/2/version/0/ayat/1/point/d> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/2/version/0/ayat/1/point/d> legal:pointHasKey "d" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/2/version/0/ayat/1/point/d/text> legal:textHasTextString "kebersamaan: dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/2/version/0/ayat/1/point/d> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/2/version/0/ayat/1/point/d/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/2/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/2/version/0/ayat/1/point/e> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/2/version/0/ayat/1/point/e> legal:pointHasKey "e" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/2/version/0/ayat/1/point/e/text> legal:textHasTextString "kemandirian." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/2/version/0/ayat/1/point/e> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/2/version/0/ayat/1/point/e/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/2/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/2/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/2/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/2/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Selain berdasarkan asas sebagaimana dimaksud pada ayat (1), penyelenggaraan Cipta Kerja dilaksanakan berdasarkan asas lain sesuai dengan bidang hukum yang diatur dalam undang-undang yang bersangkutan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/2/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/2/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/3> legal:pasalHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/3> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/3/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/3/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/3/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/3/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/3/version/0/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/3/version/0/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Undang-Undang ini dibentuk dengan tujuan untuk:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/3/version/0/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/3/version/0/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/3/version/0/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/3/version/0/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/3/version/0/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/3/version/0/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "menciptakan dan meningkatkan lapangan kerja dengan memberikan kemudahan, pelindungan, dan pemberdayaan terhadap koperasi dan UMK-M serta industri dan perdagangan nasional sebagai upaya untuk dapat menyerap tenaga kerja Indonesia yang seluas-luasnya dengan tetap memperhatikan keseimbangan dan kemajuan antardaerah dalam kesatuan ekonomi nasional," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/3/version/0/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/3/version/0/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/3/version/0/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/3/version/0/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/3/version/0/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/3/version/0/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "menjamin setiap warga negara memperoleh pekerjaan, serta mendapat imbalan dan perlakuan yang adil dan layak dalam hubungan kerja," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/3/version/0/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/3/version/0/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/3/version/0/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/3/version/0/point/c> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/3/version/0/point/c> legal:pointHasKey "c" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/3/version/0/point/c/text> legal:textHasTextString "melakukan penyesuaian berbagai aspek pengaturan yang berkaitan dengan keberpihakan, penguatan, dan perlindungan bagi koperasi dan UMK-M serta industri nasional: dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/3/version/0/point/c> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/3/version/0/point/c/text> .
