<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/3/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "rencana tata ruang pulau/kepulauanj," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/3/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/3/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/3/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/3/point/c> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/3/point/c> legal:pointHasKey "c" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/3/point/c/text> legal:textHasTextString ". rencana tata ruang kawasan strategis nasional," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/3/point/c> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/3/point/c/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/3/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/3/point/d> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/3/point/d> legal:pointHasKey "d" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/3/point/d/text> legal:textHasTextString "rencana tata ruang wilayah provinsi, dan/atau" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/3/point/d> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/3/point/d/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/3/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/15/version/0/ayat/3/point/e> .
