<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/89/version/0/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/89/version/0/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/89/version/0/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/89/version/0/point/c> .
