<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/129/version/0/ayat/4/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Dalam rangka mendukung investasi, pemegang hak pengelolaan badan bank tanah diberi kewenangan untuk:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/129/version/0/ayat/4/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/129/version/0/ayat/4/point/description> .
