<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/137/version/0/ayat/1/point/d/text> legal:textHasTextString "Badan Usaha Milik Negara/Badan Usaha Milik Daerah:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/137/version/0/ayat/1/point/d> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/137/version/0/ayat/1/point/d/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/137/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/137/version/0/ayat/1/point/e> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/137/version/0/ayat/1/point/e> legal:pointHasKey "e" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/137/version/0/ayat/1/point/e/text> legal:textHasTextString "Badan hukum milik negara/ daerah, atau" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/137/version/0/ayat/1/point/e> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/137/version/0/ayat/1/point/e/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/137/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/137/version/0/ayat/1/point/f> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/137/version/0/ayat/1/point/f> legal:pointHasKey "f" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/137/version/0/ayat/1/point/f/text> legal:textHasTextString "Badan hukum yang ditunjuk oleh Pemerintah Pusat." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/137/version/0/ayat/1/point/f> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/137/version/0/ayat/1/point/f/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/137/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/137/version/0/ayat/2> .
