<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/139/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/139/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/139/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/139/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/139/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/139/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/139/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/139/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Dalam keadaan tertentu, Pemerintah Pusat dapat membatalkan dan/atau mencabut hak pengelolaan sebagian atau seluruhnya." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/139/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/139/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/139/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/139/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/139/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/139/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Tata cara pembatalan hak pengelolaan dilaksanakan sesuai dengan ketentuan peraturan-perundang- undangan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/139/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/139/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11> legal:pasalSetHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/140> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/140> legal:pasalHasKey 140 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/140> legal:pasalHasPasalVersion <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/140/version/0> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11> legal:documentHasPasal <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/140> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/140/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasState "exists" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/140/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasCreatedTimeEpoch 0 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/140/version/0> legal:pasalVersionHasAyatSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/140/version/0/ayat> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/140/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/140/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/140/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/140/version/0/ayat/1/text> legal:textHasTextString "Dalam hal bagian bidang tanah hak pengelolaan diberikan dengan hak milik, bagian bidang tanah hak pengelolaan tersebut hapus dengan sendirinya." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/140/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/140/version/0/ayat/1/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/140/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/140/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/140/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/140/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Hak milik sebagaimana dimaksud pada ayat (1) hanya diberikan untuk keperluan rumah umum dan keperluan transmigrasi." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/140/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/140/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
