<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/144/version/0/ayat/1/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/144/version/0/ayat/1/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/144/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/144/version/0/ayat/1/point/c> .
