<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/144/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/144/version/0/ayat/1/point/d> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/144/version/0/ayat/1/point/d> legal:pointHasKey "d" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/144/version/0/ayat/1/point/d/text> legal:textHasTextString "badan hukum asing yang mempunyai perwakilan di Indonesia: atau" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/144/version/0/ayat/1/point/d> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/144/version/0/ayat/1/point/d/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/144/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/144/version/0/ayat/1/point/e> .
