<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/159/version/0/ayat/2/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "kuasa kelola:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/159/version/0/ayat/2/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/159/version/0/ayat/2/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/159/version/0/ayat/2/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/159/version/0/ayat/2/point/b> .
