<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/160/version/0/ayat/1/point/e/text> legal:textHasTextString "sumber lain yang sah." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/160/version/0/ayat/1/point/e> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/160/version/0/ayat/1/point/e/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/160/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/160/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/160/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/160/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Aset Lembaga dapat dijaminkan dalam rangka penarikan pinjaman." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/160/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/160/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/160/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/160/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/160/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/160/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pihak manapun dilarang melakukan penyitaan aset Lembaga, kecuali atas aset yang telah dijaminkan dalam rangka pinjaman." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/160/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/160/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/160/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/160/version/0/ayat/4> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/160/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasKey 4 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/160/version/0/ayat/4/text> legal:textHasTextString "Pengelolaan aset Lembaga sepenuhnya dilakukan oleh organ Lembaga berdasarkan prinsip tata kelola yang baik, akuntabel, dan transparan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/160/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/160/version/0/ayat/4/text> .
