<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/165/version/0/ayat/3/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/165/version/0/ayat/3/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "Dewan Pengawas, dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/165/version/0/ayat/3/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/165/version/0/ayat/3/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/165/version/0/ayat/3/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/165/version/0/ayat/3/point/b> .
