<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasKey 1 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/1> legal:ayatHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/1/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/1/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Dewan Pengawas sebagaimana dimaksud dalam Pasal 165 ayat (3) huruf a terdiri atas:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/1/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/1/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/1/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/1/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "Menteri yang menyelenggarakan urusan pemerintahan di bidang keuangan negara sebagai ketua merangkap anggota," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/1/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/1/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/1/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/1/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/1/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "Menteri yang menyelenggarakan urusan pemerintahan di bidang badan usaha milik negara sebagai anggota, dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/1/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/1/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/1/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/1/point/c> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/1/point/c> legal:pointHasKey "c" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/1/point/c/text> legal:textHasTextString "3 (tiga) orang yang berasal dari unsur profesional sebagai anggota." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/1/point/c> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/1/point/c/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/2> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasKey 2 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/2/text> legal:textHasTextString "Anggota Dewan Pengawas sebagaimana dimaksud pada ayat (1) diangkat dan diberhentikan oleh Presiden." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/2> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/2/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/3> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasKey 3 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/3/text> legal:textHasTextString "Untuk memilih anggota Dewan Pengawas dari unsur profesional sebagaimana dimaksud pada ayat (1) huruf c, Presiden membentuk panitia seleksi." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/3> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/3/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/4> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasKey 4 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/4> legal:ayatHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/4/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/4/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Panitia seleksi melakukan:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/4/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/4/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/4/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/4/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/4/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/4/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "pengumuman penerimaan dan pendaftaran calon," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/4/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/4/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/4/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/4/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/4/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/4/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "proses seleksi, dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/4/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/4/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/4/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/4/point/c> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/4/point/c> legal:pointHasKey "c" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/4/point/c/text> legal:textHasTextString "penyampaian nama calon kepada Presiden." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/4/point/c> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/4/point/c/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/5> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/5> legal:ayatHasKey 5 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/5/text> legal:textHasTextString "Penyampaian nama calon kepada Presiden dilakukan dalam jangka waktu paling lama 3 (tiga) bulan sejak pembentukan panitia seleksi." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/5> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/5/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/6> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/6> legal:ayatHasKey 6 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/6/text> legal:textHasTextString "Presiden menyampaikan nama calon untuk dikonsultasikan kepada Dewan Perwakilan Rakyat Republik Indonesia dalam jangka waktu paling lama 10 (sepuluh) hari kerja terhitung sejak diterimanya daftar nama calon dari panitia seleksi." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/6> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/6/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/7> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/7> legal:ayatHasKey 7 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/7/text> legal:textHasTextString "Dewan Perwakilan Rakyat Republik Indonesia menyelenggarakan sesi konsultasi dengan Presiden paling lama 10 (sepuluh) hari kerja terhitung sejak diterimanya daftar nama calon dari Presiden." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/7> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/7/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/8> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/8> legal:ayatHasKey 8 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/8/text> legal:textHasTextString "Presiden menetapkan dan mengangkat anggota Dewan Pengawas dari unsur profesional dalam jangka waktu paling lama 14 (empat belas) hari kerja terhitung sejak konsultasi sebagaimana dimaksud pada ayat (7) selesai dilaksanakan." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/8> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/8/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/9> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/9> legal:ayatHasKey 9 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/9/text> legal:textHasTextString "Dalam hal sesi konsultasi tidak terlaksana sesuai jangka waktu yang ditentukan sebagaimana dimaksud pada ayat (7), Presiden menetapkan dan mengangkat anggota Dewan Pengawas dari unsur profesional dalam jangka waktu paling lama 14 (empat belas) hari kerja sebagaimana dimaksud pada ayat (8)." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/9> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/9/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/10> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/10> legal:ayatHasKey 10 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/10/text> legal:textHasTextString "Ketentuan lebih lanjut mengenai seleksi anggota Dewan Pengawas dari unsur profesional diatur dalam Peraturan Pemerintah." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/10> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/10/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/11> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/11> legal:ayatHasKey 11 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/11/text> legal:textHasTextString "Sesama anggota Dewan Pengawas dilarang saling memiliki hubungan keluarga sampai derajat kedua atau besan dengan sesama anggota Dewan Pengawas dan/atau dengan anggota Dewan Direktur." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/11> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/11/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/12> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/12> legal:ayatHasKey 12 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/12/text> legal:textHasTextString "Anggota Dewan Pengawas dari unsur profesional diangkat untuk masa jabatan 5 (lima) tahun dan hanya dapat diangkat kembali untuk 1 (satu) kali masa jabatan berikutnya." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/12> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/12/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/13> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/13> legal:ayatHasKey 13 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/13> legal:ayatHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/13/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/13/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Dalam rangka pengangkatan anggota Dewan Pengawas dari unsur profesional untuk pertama kali, Presiden menetapkan masa jabatan 3 (tiga) anggota Dewan Pengawas sebagai berikut:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/13/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/13/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/13/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/13/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/13/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/13/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "1 (satu) anggota diangkat untuk masa jabatan 5 (lima) tahun," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/13/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/13/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/13/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/13/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/13/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/13/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "1 (satu) anggota diangkat untuk masa jabatan 4 (empat) tahun, dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/13/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/13/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/13/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/13/point/c> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/13/point/c> legal:pointHasKey "c" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/13/point/c/text> legal:textHasTextString "1 (satu) anggota diangkat untuk masa jabatan 3 (tiga) tahun." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/13/point/c> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/13/point/c/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/14> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/14> legal:ayatHasKey 14 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/14/text> legal:textHasTextString "Dewan Pengawas sebagaimana dimaksud pada ayat (1) bertugas melakukan pengawasan atas penyelenggaraan Lembaga Pengelola Investasi oleh Dewan Direktur." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/14> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/14/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15> legal:ayatHasKey 15 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15> legal:ayatHasPointSet <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/description> legal:textHasTextString "Dalam melaksanakan tugas sebagaimana dimaksud pada ayat (14) Dewan Pengawas berwenang:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point> legal:pointSetHasDescription <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/description> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/a> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/a> legal:pointHasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/a/text> legal:textHasTextString "menyetujui rencana kerja dan anggaran tahunan beserta indikator kinerja utama (key performance indicator) yang diusulkan Dewan Direktur," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/b/text> legal:textHasTextString "melakukan evaluasi pencapaian indikator kinerja utama (key performance indicator)," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/b> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/b/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/c> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/c> legal:pointHasKey "c" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/c/text> legal:textHasTextString ". menerima dan mengevaluasi laporan pertanggungjawaban dari Dewan Direktur," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/c> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/c/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/d> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/d> legal:pointHasKey "d" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/d/text> legal:textHasTextString "menyampaikan laporan pertanggungjawaban Dewan Pengawas dan Dewan Direktur kepada Presiden," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/d> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/d/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/e> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/e> legal:pointHasKey "e" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/e/text> legal:textHasTextString "menetapkan dan mengangkat anggota Dewan Penasihat," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/e> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/e/text> .
