<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/f> legal:pointHasKey "f" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/f/text> legal:textHasTextString "' mengangkat dan memberhentikan Dewan Direktur:" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/f> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/f/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/g> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/g> legal:pointHasKey "g" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/g/text> legal:textHasTextString "menetapkan remunerasi Dewan Pengawas dan Dewan Direktur," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/g> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/g/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/h> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/h> legal:pointHasKey "h" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/h/text> legal:textHasTextString "mengusulkan peningkatan dan/atau pengurangan modal Lembaga kepada Presiden," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/h> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/h/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/i> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/i> legal:pointHasKey "i" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/i/text> legal:textHasTextString "menyetujui laporan keuangan tahunan Lembaga," .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/i> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/i/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/j> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/j> legal:pointHasKey "j" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/j/text> legal:textHasTextString "memberhentikan sementara satu atau lebih anggota Dewan Direktur dan menunjuk pengganti sementara untuk Dewan Direktur: dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/j> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/j/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/k> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/k> legal:pointHasKey "k" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/k/text> legal:textHasTextString "menyetujui penunjukan auditor Lembaga." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/k> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/15/point/k/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat> legal:ayatSetHasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/16> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/16> legal:ayatHasKey 16 .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/16/text> legal:textHasTextString "Untuk membantu Dewan Pengawas dalam melaksanakan tugas dan wewenangnya, Dewan Pengawas dapat membentuk komite." .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/16> legal:ayatHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/166/version/0/ayat/16/text> .
