<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/184/version/0/point/a> legal:pointHasText <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/184/version/0/point/a/text> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/184/version/0/point> legal:pointSetHasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/184/version/0/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/184/version/0/point/b> legal:pointHasKey "b" .
